(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-arlen-electric-leather-recliner', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Arlen Electric Leather Recliner', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 4376, 1531.6, 1, 1531.6, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-arlen-electric-leather-recliner-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-arlen-electric-leather-recliner-2.webp'], 'Single New-condition Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Arlen electric leather recliner, unmanifested at $1,531.60 against a $4,376 retail reference. Power-reclining leather chairs sell quickly through designer-resale boutiques, home-theater flippers, and local Facebook Marketplace listings where buyers test the motion before paying. The electric mechanism plus genuine leather is the value story for resellers writing copy. On intake, plug in the recliner and cycle the mechanism fully once to confirm motor and power supply both work, then inspect the leather on seat and arm contact points for transit creasing. Photograph the control and the leather tag. Freight is single-piece LTL or local box-truck pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 85),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-arlen-electric-recliner-with-vintage-chenille', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Arlen Electric Recliner with Vintage Chenille', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 3176, 1111.6, 1, 1111.6, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-arlen-electric-recliner-with-vintage-chenille-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-arlen-electric-recliner-with-vintage-chenille-2.webp'], 'Single New-condition Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Arlen electric recliner in Vintage Chenille, unmanifested at $1,111.60 against a $3,176 retail reference. Power-reclining accent chairs in textured upholstery move through designer-resale shops, home-theater flippers, and local Facebook Marketplace buyers who can test the motion in person. The chenille texture differentiates it from generic leather recliners and gives resellers a clear copy angle. On intake, plug in and cycle the mechanism end to end to confirm the motor and transformer both work, then vacuum the chenille and photograph the fabric tag. Freight is single-piece LTL or local box-truck pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 86),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Arlen Leather Recliner', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 4176, 1461.6, 1, 1461.6, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-2.webp'], 'Single New-condition Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Arlen leather recliner, unmanifested at $1,461.60 against a $4,176 retail reference. Manual leather recliners sit in a slightly different lane than power versions: the buyer pool widens to include households avoiding electrical complexity, plus short-term rental operators who do not want plug placement to dictate furniture layout. Designer-resale shops, Chairish, and local Facebook Marketplace are the cleanest channels, with marketplace closing fastest on pickup. On intake, cycle the reclining mechanism by hand to confirm smooth travel and lockout, then inspect the leather at seat and arm contact points. Freight is single-piece LTL or local box-truck pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 87),
(null, 'bradley-bookcase', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Bradley Bookcase - 65% Off Retail Price', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 2250, 787.5, 1, 787.5, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/bradley-bookcase-1.webp','/images/products/bradley-bookcase-2.webp'], 'One New-condition Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Bradley bookcase, unmanifested at $787.50 against a $2,250 retail reference. Tall casegood bookcases at this grade sell into interior designers, home-office flippers, and staging companies that need a single anchoring shelf unit rather than a matched pair. Channels include Chairish, 1stDibs Trade, and local Facebook Marketplace where buyers can pick up rather than freight a tall, narrow piece. On intake, stand the carton upright to inspect for shipping damage at the top corners, confirm all adjustable shelf pins and hardware are bagged inside, and photograph the finish under daylight. Freight is single-piece LTL or local box-truck pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 88),
(null, 'butler-king-headboard-w-performance-velvet', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Butler King Headboard w/ Performance Velvet - 65% Off Retail Price', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 4463, 1562.05, 1, 1562.05, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/butler-king-headboard-w-performance-velvet-1.webp','/images/products/butler-king-headboard-w-performance-velvet-2.webp'], 'One New-condition Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Butler king headboard in Performance Velvet, unmanifested at $1,562.05 against a $4,463 retail reference. King headboards in performance velvet sell into interior designers, short-term rental operators, and designer-resale shops where the velvet texture reads as luxury but the performance backing survives real households. Chairish and 1stDibs Trade reach trade buyers; local Facebook Marketplace closes pickup sales faster on a piece this size. On intake, lay the headboard flat, vacuum the velvet against the nap to spot any transit pressure marks, and confirm the bolt-on hardware is bagged to the back. Freight is single-piece LTL or local box-truck pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 89),
(null, 'cacon-wxe-no-welt-softa-w-performance-cross-weave', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Cacon Wxe No Welt Softa w/ Performance Cross Weave - 65% Off Retail Price', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'new', 10247, 3586.45, 1, 3586.45, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/cacon-wxe-no-welt-softa-w-performance-cross-weave-1.webp','/images/products/cacon-wxe-no-welt-softa-w-performance-cross-weave-2.webp'], 'Single-unit New, unmanifested designer sofa from the Cacon Wxe line with a no-welt silhouette and performance cross-weave upholstery rated for high-traffic residential use. Retail tag sits at 10,247 against a 3,586.45 buy, leaving meaningful room for resellers flipping premium furniture through Facebook Marketplace, Chairish, AptDeco, or a brick-and-mortar consignment showroom that caters to interior designers and staging firms. Performance fabric expands the buyer pool to households with kids and pets, which shortens days-on-market. Inspect frame joinery, cushion fill, and weave for any transit marks at intake, photograph from multiple angles in natural light, and confirm freight class plus liftgate before scheduling dock pickup.', 90),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-callan-48-bench-performance-linen', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Callan 48 Bench Performance Linen', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 2100, 735, 1, 735, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-callan-48-bench-performance-linen-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-callan-48-bench-performance-linen-2.webp'], 'One New, unmanifested 48-inch Callan bench from Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams upholstered in performance linen, landing at a 735 cost against a 2,100 retail. Benches in this size move well through staging companies, boutique furniture stores, and design-forward Marketplace and Chairish listings where buyers want an entry, end-of-bed, or window seat that holds up to daily use. Performance linen widens the audience to family households and short-term rental operators. At intake, unwrap carefully, check legs and apron for shipping scuffs, photograph the linen weave up close, and stage in a clean setting before listing; arrange freight pickup with blanket wrap to protect the upholstery.', 91),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-chair-with-performance-vintage-velvet', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Cara Chair with Performance Vintage Velvet', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 2117, 740.95, 1, 740.95, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-chair-with-performance-vintage-velvet-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-chair-with-performance-vintage-velvet-2.webp'], 'A single New, unmanifested Cara accent chair upholstered in performance vintage velvet, picked up for 740.95 against a 2,117 retail. Velvet accent chairs are a strong fit for interior designers, staging firms, and Chairish or 1stDibs-style resellers chasing a statement piece for living rooms and home offices; performance treatment makes it viable for families and rental properties too. Listings photograph well under warm light, which lifts perceived value on Marketplace and Instagram. At intake, inspect the velvet nap for pressure marks from packaging, brush in one direction, verify swivel or leg hardware is tight, and palletize for blanket-wrap freight rather than parcel.', 92),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-leather-tall-full-swivel-chair', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Cara Leather Tall Full Swivel Chair', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 3687, 1290.45, 1, 1290.45, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-leather-tall-full-swivel-chair-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-leather-tall-full-swivel-chair-2.webp'], 'One New, unmanifested Cara tall full swivel chair in leather, with a 1,290.45 cost set against a 3,687 retail. Leather swivels carry a defined buyer in the secondary market: home-office buyers, executives outfitting reading nooks, and design firms sourcing for client projects, with strong demand on Chairish, 1stDibs, and high-end Facebook Marketplace listings. Leather also lets you target male-skewed audiences that pay premiums for materials. At intake, condition the leather lightly if it reads dry from shipping, test the swivel mechanism through a full rotation, photograph the grain and stitching tightly, and crate or blanket-wrap for outbound freight rather than risking parcel damage.', 93),
(null, 'cara-queen-sleeper-sofa', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Cara Queen Sleeper Sofa - 65% Off Retail Price', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 5500, 1925, 1, 1925, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/cara-queen-sleeper-sofa-1.webp','/images/products/cara-queen-sleeper-sofa-2.webp'], 'A single New, unmanifested Cara queen sleeper sofa, costing 1,925 against a 5,500 retail. Sleeper sofas pull a wider buyer pool than standard sofas: short-term rental hosts, small-apartment buyers, in-law suite outfitters, and basement renovators all search this category specifically, which shortens listing time on Marketplace, OfferUp, and Chairish. The Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams nameplate, already in the title, supports a stronger ask than generic sleepers. At intake, deploy the mechanism fully to verify the bar and mattress are sound, photograph it both folded and opened, and book blanket-wrap LTL freight or local box-truck pickup, since sleeper weight rules out standard parcel.', 94),
(null, 'cara-queen-sleeper-sofa-1', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Cara Queen Sleeper Sofa - 65% Off Retail Price', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 5500, 1925, 1, 1925, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/cara-queen-sleeper-sofa-1-1.webp','/images/products/cara-queen-sleeper-sofa-1-2.webp'], 'Second New, unmanifested Cara queen sleeper sofa unit at 1,925 cost against a 5,500 retail. Having two identical sleepers gives a reseller pricing flexibility: list one at full ask to anchor the market and a second slightly below to close quickly, or sell as a pair to a short-term rental operator outfitting multiple units. Staging companies and small-hotel buyers occasionally take duplicates for matching guest rooms. Treat each unit on its own dock receipt, open the mechanism, inspect the mattress and frame, and photograph separately so listings reflect actual condition. Plan blanket-wrap LTL or local box-truck pickup; sleeper weight rules out parcel.', 95),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-tall-back-chair', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Cara Tall Back Chair', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 2117, 740.95, 1, 740.95, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-tall-back-chair-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-tall-back-chair-2.webp'], 'One New, unmanifested Cara tall back chair from the Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams line at 740.95 cost against a 2,117 retail. Tall-back accent chairs read as statement pieces in living rooms and reading nooks, which lines up well with interior designers, staging firms, and design-savvy Chairish or Marketplace buyers. Higher-back silhouettes also photograph well as solo hero shots on Instagram and Pinterest, which lifts engagement and ask price. At intake, inspect upholstery for transit pressure marks, confirm legs and frame are tight, dust the fabric or vacuum lightly, and palletize with blanket wrap for LTL freight; avoid parcel due to seat-cushion crush risk.', 96),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-tall-back-chair-1', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Cara Tall Back Chair', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 2744, 960.4, 1, 960.4, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-tall-back-chair-1-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-cara-tall-back-chair-1-2.webp'], 'Second New, unmanifested Cara tall back chair, this one at 960.40 cost against a 2,744 retail tag, suggesting a different fabric or finish from the prior unit even under the same model name. Higher cost basis still leaves margin for design-trade resellers, staging firms, and Chairish-class buyers who want the silhouette in a premium fabric. Treat the listing on its own merits rather than pairing with the lower-cost twin, since fabric drives ask price. At intake, identify and document the upholstery, inspect for shipping marks, confirm the frame and legs sit flat, and palletize for blanket-wrap LTL pickup at the dock.', 97),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-carson-92-sofa-with-performance-textured-two-tone', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Carson 92 Sofa with Performance Textured Two Tone', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 5500, 1925, 1, 1925, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-carson-92-sofa-with-performance-textured-two-tone-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-carson-92-sofa-with-performance-textured-two-tone-2.webp'], 'A single New, unmanifested Carson 92-inch sofa upholstered in a performance textured two-tone fabric, costing 1,925 against a 5,500 retail. Ninety-two-inch sofas are the workhorse size for living rooms, which gives them the deepest buyer pool on Facebook Marketplace, Chairish, and AptDeco; performance fabric and the two-tone styling widen the audience to families, short-term rental operators, and staging firms. Photograph the texture detail tight and a wide hero shot. At intake, inspect cushion seams and the back deck, verify all feet are tight, vacuum the upholstery, and book blanket-wrap LTL freight rather than parcel for outbound pickup.', 98),
(null, 'celina-king-bed-w-tall-headboard-performance-velvet', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Celina King Bed w/Tall Headboard + Performance Velvet - 65% Off Retail Price', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 4463, 1562.05, 1, 1562.05, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/celina-king-bed-w-tall-headboard-performance-velvet-1.webp','/images/products/celina-king-bed-w-tall-headboard-performance-velvet-2.webp'], 'One New, unmanifested Celina king bed with a tall headboard upholstered in performance velvet, picked up for 1,562.05 against a 4,463 retail. Upholstered king beds with a statement headboard pull premium prices through Chairish, 1stDibs-style resellers, design-trade showrooms, and Facebook Marketplace in higher-income ZIPs; performance velvet brings family and short-term rental buyers into the same listing. The tall headboard makes the hero shot worth the staging time. At intake, unbox slats and rails carefully, inspect velvet for crush or transit marks, brush the nap in one direction, confirm bolt hardware is complete, and palletize for blanket-wrap LTL outbound.', 99),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-celina-king-bed-with-performance-linen', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Celina King Bed with Performance Linen', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'new', 4636, 1622.6, 1, 1622.6, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-celina-king-bed-with-performance-linen-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-celina-king-bed-with-performance-linen-2.webp'], 'A single New, unmanifested Celina king bed upholstered in performance linen, with a 1,622.60 cost against a 4,636 retail. Upholstered king beds in neutral linen tones move quickly through staging companies, short-term rental operators, design-trade resellers, and Marketplace buyers furnishing primary bedrooms. Performance treatment on the linen broadens the listing to families and rental properties that would normally avoid woven fabrics. At intake, unbox slats, rails, and headboard separately, inspect the linen for shipping creases or marks, vacuum lightly, verify all bolt hardware is bagged with the unit, and palletize for blanket-wrap LTL outbound rather than risking parcel on the headboard panel.', 100),
(null, 'mitchell-gold-bob-williams-celina-king-bed-with-performance-linen-1', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Celina Queen Headboard Only with Performance Linen', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 2600, 910, 1, 910, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-celina-king-bed-with-performance-linen-1-1.webp','/images/products/mitchell-gold-bob-williams-celina-king-bed-with-performance-linen-1-2.webp'], 'One New, unmanifested Celina queen headboard-only piece in performance linen, costing 910 against a 2,600 retail. Headboard-only listings target buyers who already own a queen frame and want a fast upholstered refresh, which is a strong fit for Marketplace, OfferUp, and Chairish; staging companies sometimes take them too for partial room refreshes. Single-piece headboards also ship cheaper than full bed sets, which improves outbound margin. At intake, unwrap and inspect the linen for transit creases, confirm mounting hardware is bagged and complete, photograph the front face cleanly, and palletize or blanket-wrap for LTL or local box-truck pickup.', 101),
(null, 'celina-queen-bed-frame', 'Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams Celina Queen Headboard w/ Vinyl - 65% Off Retail Price', 'furniture', 'unmanifested', 'new', 4163, 1457.05, 1, 1457.05, 'in-stock', array['/images/products/celina-queen-bed-frame-1.webp','/images/products/celina-queen-bed-frame-2.webp'], 'A single New, unmanifested Celina queen headboard in vinyl, costing 1,457.05 against a 4,163 retail. Vinyl upholstery widens the target buyer to short-term rental operators, hospitality groups, and family households that want easy-clean surfaces, while still photographing as a leather-look hero piece for Marketplace and Chairish listings. The Mitchell Gold + Bob Williams nameplate, already in the title, supports a premium ask versus generic vinyl headboards. At intake, inspect the vinyl for scuffs or pressure marks from packaging, wipe down with a damp cloth, confirm mounting hardware is present and bagged, and palletize for blanket-wrap LTL or local dock pickup.', 102),
