(null, '200-units-mixed-perfume-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'Mixed Perfume Pallet, 200 Units', 'health-beauty', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1000, 1000, 200, 5, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/200-units-mixed-perfume-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp'], 'Two hundred unmanifested units of mixed-brand fragrance from customer returns, spanning designer-style EDT and EDP, body sprays, mists, rollerballs, and gift sets across men''s, women''s, and unisex at $5 per bottle. The mix runs high enough on margin and deep enough on rotation to support continuous listings on eBay, Mercari, and live fragrance shows, where individual bottles routinely clear several multiples of cost. Gift sets carry well into Q4 promotions. On intake, separate by gender and bottle size, then verify seals and fill levels before pulling the gift sets into a holiday-staged bin. Pickup is from the Jacksonville, FL dock.', 187),
