(null, '180-units-mixed-perfume-pallet-medium-lot', 'Mixed Perfume Pallet, 180 Units', 'health-beauty', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1000, 1000, 180, 5.56, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/180-units-mixed-perfume-pallet-medium-lot-1.webp'], 'One hundred eighty unmanifested units of fragrance from customer returns, weighted toward fast-moving body sprays, mists, rollerballs, and travel minis with designer-style EDT and EDP anchoring the higher end at $5.56 per bottle. The skew toward smaller formats fits market vendors and live sellers who move volume on impulse pricing rather than ticket size, with rollerballs and minis pricing cleanly into bundle-of-three or grab-bag formats. Anchor bottles support headline pricing on shows. On intake, separate minis from full-size bottles, verify seals, and stage the rollerballs and travel sizes into pre-built bundles before listing. Pickup is from the Jacksonville, FL dock.', 189),
(null, '280-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'Lululemon Clothes Pallet, 280 Units NWT', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1400, 1400, 310, 4.52, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/280-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp','/images/savemore/280-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-wholesale-lot-2.webp','/images/savemore/280-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-wholesale-lot-3.webp','/images/savemore/280-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-wholesale-lot-4.webp','/images/savemore/280-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-wholesale-lot-5.webp','/images/savemore/280-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-wholesale-lot-6.webp','/images/savemore/280-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-wholesale-lot-7.webp'], 'Three hundred ten units of authentic, new-with-tags Lululemon activewear from customer returns at $4.52 per piece on an unmanifested mid-tier pallet. Individual-piece resale in this brand routinely lands well into the double and low triple digits on Poshmark, Mercari, and eBay, which makes the per-piece economics here unusually strong for an activewear specialty seller building inventory around a single premium label. Live sellers can run brand-only shows on the depth alone. On intake, sort by garment type and size, verify tag presence on each piece, and photograph the higher-margin bottoms first to seed listings. Pickup is from the Jacksonville, FL dock.', 190),
(null, '150-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-large-lot', 'Lululemon Activewear Pallet, 150 Units', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 920, 920, 310, 2.97, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-large-lot-1.webp','/images/savemore/150-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-large-lot-2.webp','/images/savemore/150-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-large-lot-3.webp','/images/savemore/150-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-large-lot-4.webp','/images/savemore/150-units-lululemon-clothes-pallet-large-lot-5.webp'], 'An entry-tier unmanifested pallet of three hundred ten units of authentic, new-with-tags Lululemon activewear from customer returns at $2.97 per piece. The volume economics work for resellers testing the brand-specialty model before stepping into truckload buying, with enough depth across tops, bottoms, and layering pieces to support steady single-piece listings on Poshmark, Mercari, and eBay where the label commands strong individual ticket prices. Live sellers can run dedicated brand shows. On intake, sort by garment type and size, verify tags on each piece, and route any tagless or damaged units into a separate grade-B bundle. Pickup is from the Jacksonville, FL dock.', 191),
(null, '200-units-mixed-shoes-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'Mixed Shoes Pallet, 200 Pairs', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 790, 790, 200, 3.95, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/200-units-mixed-shoes-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp'], 'Two hundred pairs of inspected mixed footwear from customer returns at $3.95 per pair, covering athletic and running, sneakers, casual and dress, and seasonal styles across men''s, women''s, and kids'' sizes. The blend of overstock, shelf-pull, and clean returns lands mostly new or near-new, which makes it workable for booth sellers, flea markets, and eBay stores that move shoes by size run rather than brand. The category breadth supports steady listing velocity. On intake, sort by gender first, then by size and category, and band pairs together immediately to avoid singles. Pickup is from the Jacksonville, FL dock; LTL freight quotes available on request.', 192),
(null, '200-units-mixed-toy-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'Mixed Toy Pallet, 200 Units', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 600, 600, 200, 3, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/200-units-mixed-toy-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp'], 'Two hundred mixed toys from customer returns spanning action figures, dolls, board games, puzzles, plush, and activity sets across every price tier at $3 per unit. The blend of overstock, shelf-pull, and clean returns in retail packaging is built for fourth-quarter holiday volume through flea markets, Facebook Marketplace, and bin store rotations, where toy demand spikes hard from October through December. Live sellers can also run toy-themed shows on the breadth. On intake, sort by age range and category first, then pull anything licensed or seasonal into a Q4-staged bin and route opened-box pieces into a discount bundle. Pickup is from the Jacksonville, FL dock.', 193),
(null, '150-units-mixed-toy-pallet-large-lot', 'Mixed Toy Pallet, 150 Units (Large Lot)', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 800, 800, 150, 5.33, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-mixed-toy-pallet-large-lot-1.webp'], 'One hundred fifty units of customer-return toys skewed toward branded and licensed product at $5.33 per unit, including figures, vehicles, play sets, mid and large-format games, building sets, and premium plush. The heavier per-unit mix carries higher individual ticket potential than basic mixed-toy pallets, which makes it workable year-round for eBay sellers and specialty toy resellers rather than purely a holiday play. The licensed content supports stronger search-driven listings. On intake, sort by license and category first, verify box condition on the larger sets, and pull the strongest pieces for individual listings while bundling smaller items into themed grab bags. Pickup is from the Jacksonville, FL dock.', 194),
(null, '200-units-electronics-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'Mixed Electronics Pallet, 200 Units', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1500, 1500, 200, 7.5, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/200-units-electronics-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp'], 'This 200-unit consumer electronics pallet is an unmanifested customer-return lot covering headphones, earbuds, speakers, soundbars, chargers, cables, power banks, and assorted smart-home and small device gear. At $1,500 the cost lands at $7.50 per unit, leaving working margin even after grading time. Targets eBay and Mercari resellers, flea-market booths, and bin-store operators who price-tier mixed tech and turn it weekly. The sealed-share moves first online while returns get cycled through a test bench. On intake, sort sealed from opened, then power-test the returns category by category before listing or pricing the bench. Pickup available from the Jacksonville dock or freight-quoted to your warehouse.', 195),
(null, '150-units-electronics-pallet-large-lot', 'Electronics Pallet, 150 Units (Large Lot)', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1000, 1000, 150, 6.67, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-electronics-pallet-large-lot-1.webp'], 'A 150-unit consumer electronics lot weighted toward headphones, earbuds, speakers, wearables, tablets, streaming sticks, and smart-home gear, sold unmanifested in customer-return condition. At $1,000 the per-unit cost is $6.67, a workable basis for resellers scaling tested-electronics inventory across eBay, Mercari, OfferUp, and local marketplace listings. The device weighting favors higher ticket items where one strong sale covers several bench hours. Build an intake lane that separates sealed from opened, charges and boots each returned device, and segments good, parts, and scrap before listing. Available for Jacksonville dock pickup or freight quote on request, with no appointment needed for confirmed orders.', 196),
(null, '150-units-electronics-pallet-medium-lot', 'Electronics Pallet, 150 Units (Medium Lot)', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 800, 800, 150, 5.33, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-electronics-pallet-medium-lot-1.webp'], 'A value-tier 150-unit electronics lot weighted toward chargers, cables, cases, power banks, hubs, entry-level audio, and small smart-home gadgets, sold unmanifested in customer-return condition. At $800 the per-unit basis is $5.33, which suits newer resellers who need fast-testing items that ship cheap via first-class mail or padded mailer. Strong fit for eBay lots, Mercari bundles, Amazon FBM listings, and flea-market accessory tables where small items move on impulse. On intake, batch by category, test cables and chargers with a USB meter, and bundle low-ticket pieces into multi-packs for better price-per-listing. Dock pickup or LTL freight from Jacksonville.', 197),
(null, '200-units-kitchen-appliance-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'Kitchen Appliance Pallet, 200 Units', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1500, 1500, 200, 7.5, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/200-units-kitchen-appliance-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp'], 'A 200-unit kitchen appliance pallet of countertop electrics covering air fryers, toaster ovens, blenders, food processors, mixers, coffee makers, espresso machines, and specialty pieces, sold unmanifested in customer-return condition with many units still sealed. At $1,500 the cost works out to $7.50 per unit, giving room for a quick power-on test cycle on the returns share. Targets Facebook Marketplace, OfferUp, and bin-store operators plus flea-market dealers who can move mid-ticket housewares fast. On intake, plug-test each returned unit, sort by working, missing-parts, and scrap, and stage sealed units first. Jacksonville dock pickup or freight quote on request.', 198),
(null, '150-units-kitchen-appliance-pallet-large-lot', 'Kitchen Appliance Pallet, 150 Units (Large Lot)', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1000, 1000, 150, 6.67, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-kitchen-appliance-pallet-large-lot-1.webp','/images/savemore/150-units-kitchen-appliance-pallet-large-lot-2.webp'], '150 small electrics weighted toward mid-size, branded countertop pieces, covering air fryers, multi-cookers, full-size blenders and stand mixers, plus drip, pod, and espresso machines. Unmanifested customer returns at $1,000, landing the per-unit basis at $6.67 with mid-ticket retail price points behind it. Fits resellers scaling past a first buy on Facebook Marketplace, OfferUp, and local pickup channels where larger kitchen items move on photos and short test videos. On intake, run a power-on and seal check, separate units with cords or accessories missing into a parts bin, and stage tested working units for immediate listing. Jacksonville dock pickup or freight booking available.', 199),
(null, '120-units-kitchen-appliance-pallet-medium-lot', 'Kitchen Appliance Pallet, 120 Units (Medium Lot)', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 800, 800, 120, 6.67, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/120-units-kitchen-appliance-pallet-medium-lot-1.webp'], 'A starter pallet of 120 compact countertop electrics covering air fryers, toasters, single-serve cookers, personal blenders, hand mixers, coffee makers, kettles, and pod machines across recognizable brand names. Sold unmanifested in customer-return condition at $800, a $6.67 per-unit basis well suited to a first-time houseware reseller building a routine. Good fit for Facebook Marketplace, OfferUp, weekend yard-sale lots, and small flea-market tables where price tags under $40 move fastest. On intake, plug-test each unit, separate working stock from parts donors, and bundle missing-accessory pieces into lower-tier listings. Jacksonville dock pickup or LTL freight quote available.', 200),
(null, '150-units-milwaukee-tools-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'Milwaukee Tools Pallet, 150 Units', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 2000, 2000, 150, 13.33, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-milwaukee-tools-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp'], 'A 150-unit Milwaukee-focused lot built around M18 and M12 cordless drills, drivers, and impact tools, plus batteries, chargers, bare tools, hand tools, and jobsite gear. Unmanifested customer returns priced at $2,000, putting per-unit cost at $13.33 against a category that holds strong resale value on eBay, OfferUp, and local trades-focused Facebook groups. Cordless red-brand tools draw contractor and serious DIY buyers who pay for working units and battery health. On intake, charge and meter every battery, run each cordless tool under load, and grade by working, parts, and accessory-only. Jacksonville dock pickup or palletized freight on request.', 201),
(null, '150-units-milwaukee-tools-pallet-large-lot', 'Milwaukee Tools Pallet, 150 Units (Large Lot)', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1900, 1900, 150, 12.67, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-milwaukee-tools-pallet-large-lot-1.webp'], 'A broad 150-unit Milwaukee mix spanning M18 and M12 cordless tools, hand tools, accessories, blades, bits, storage, and jobsite gear, sold unmanifested in customer-return condition. At $1,900 the cost-per-unit lands at $12.67, giving a tool reseller more listings and price points off one buy versus a tight cordless-only lot. Fits eBay store operators, trade Facebook groups, and flea-market tool tables where accessories cross-sell into cordless purchases. On intake, sort cordless from hand tools and accessories, function-test each battery and motor, and pack blade and bit sets for bundled listings. Jacksonville dock pickup or LTL freight quote available.', 202),
