(null, '200-units-dewalt-tools-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'DeWalt Tools Pallet, 200 Units', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 2000, 2000, 200, 10, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/200-units-dewalt-tools-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp'], 'A 200-unit DeWalt lot built around 20V MAX and FLEXVOLT cordless drills, drivers, and saws, plus batteries, chargers, bare tools, hand tools, accessories, and jobsite gear. Unmanifested customer returns priced at $2,000, landing per-unit cost at $10 across a brand contractors and DIY buyers search by name. Strong fit for eBay tool stores, OfferUp, local trade Facebook groups, and flea-market booths positioned near hardware traffic. On intake, function-test each cordless tool under load, meter every battery, and split working from parts and bare items. Sized for a reseller with bench time and a battery-grading workflow. Jacksonville dock pickup or palletized LTL freight on request.', 204),
(null, '150-units-dewalt-tools-pallet-large-lot', 'DeWalt Tools Pallet, 150 Units', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1700, 1700, 150, 11.33, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-dewalt-tools-pallet-large-lot-1.webp','/images/savemore/150-units-dewalt-tools-pallet-large-lot-2.webp'], 'A broad DeWalt mix of 150 units blending 20V MAX cordless tools and drivers with hand tools, bits, blades, and jobsite gear, sold unmanifested in customer-return condition. At $1,700 the per-unit cost is $11.33, giving a tool reseller wide listings and price points across one of the most-searched names in the trades. Fits eBay store operators, OfferUp sellers, and trade-focused Facebook marketplace listings where yellow-brand demand holds steady. On intake, segment cordless from hand tools and accessories, load-test each motor, and meter every battery for runtime before grading working, parts, or accessory-only. Jacksonville dock pickup or LTL freight quote available.', 205),
(null, '200-units-ryobi-tools-pallet-wholesale-lot', 'Ryobi Tools Pallet, 200 Units', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1750, 1750, 200, 8.75, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/200-units-ryobi-tools-pallet-wholesale-lot-1.webp'], 'A 200-unit Ryobi wholesale lot covering ONE+ 18V drills, drivers, saws, and yard tools alongside bare tools, batteries, chargers, hand tools, and accessories. Sold unmanifested in customer-return condition at $1,750, putting the per-unit basis under $9 across a brand built around a deep DIY and homeowner buyer base. Targets eBay, OfferUp, Facebook Marketplace, and weekend flea-market tool tables, where ONE+ ecosystem buyers shop for bare tools and battery add-ons. On intake, charge every battery, function-test each cordless unit, and separate bare tools into a bundle lane to cross-sell with batteries. Jacksonville dock pickup or palletized LTL freight on request.', 206),
(null, '150-units-ryobi-tools-pallet-large-lot', 'Ryobi Tools Pallet, 150 Units', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1250, 1250, 150, 8.33, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/150-units-ryobi-tools-pallet-large-lot-1.webp'], 'A 150-unit Ryobi lot pairing ONE+ 18V cordless tools with batteries, chargers, hand tools, accessories, and seasonal gear, sold unmanifested in customer-return condition. At $1,250 the cost-per-unit lands at $8.33, a high-volume basis for resellers serving the broad ONE+ ecosystem that draws homeowner and DIY buyers. Targets eBay, OfferUp, Facebook Marketplace, and local yard-sale and flea-market tool tables where lower-ticket cordless tools turn weekly. On intake, charge and meter each battery, load-test the cordless bodies, and group bare tools into ecosystem bundles that price higher than singles. Jacksonville dock pickup or LTL freight booking available on request.', 207),
('MBA-BULK-20PCS', 'macbook-air-pallets', 'MacBook Air Liquidation Pallet, Apple Laptops', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1800, 1800, 1, 1800, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/macbook-air-pallets-1.webp'], 'A wholesale Apple laptop lot of assorted MacBook Air units across recent generations, mixed Intel and Apple-silicon, sold unmanifested as a customer-return buy at $1,800. Built for refurbishers and tech resellers with the bench skill to diagnose, recondition, and grade, then route units through eBay, Back Market, Swappa, and local refurb storefronts where Apple laptops command tested-and-graded pricing. Expect a spread of working, repairable, and parts-only condition, sold as-is. On intake, log serials, run hardware diagnostics, check battery cycle counts and screen condition, and grade each unit before pricing or pulling for parts harvest. Jacksonville dock pickup or freight quote available.', 208),
(null, 'sneakers-pallet', 'Mixed-Brand Sneakers Pallet, 60 to 80 Pairs', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1100, 1100, 80, 13.75, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/sneakers-pallet-1.webp'], 'A mixed-brand sneaker pallet of 60 to 80 pairs spanning Nike, Adidas, Puma, New Balance, Reebok, Asics, Skechers, Vans, and Converse, sold unmanifested in customer-return condition at $1,100. Per-pair cost lands at $13.75 against a category that moves through bin-store grab tables, swap-meet booths, warehouse-sale racks, and Facebook Marketplace lots where mixed-size variety is the draw. Authentic, recognizable brand mix supports walk-up impulse buys and bundled multi-pair pricing. On intake, sort by size and brand, pair up singles where possible, and stage cosmetically clean pairs for top-tier display while routing scuffed pairs into a bin-priced tier. Jacksonville dock pickup or LTL freight on request.', 209),
(null, 'iphone-14-pro-max-pallet', 'Premium Smartphone Liquidation Pallet, 150 Units', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 2500, 2500, 150, 16.67, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/iphone-14-pro-max-pallet-1.webp','/images/savemore/iphone-14-pro-max-pallet-2.webp','/images/savemore/iphone-14-pro-max-pallet-3.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of 150 premium smartphone handsets priced at $2,500, or about $16.67 per unit, in mixed storage tiers and finishes typical of carrier and big-box returns. This is a refurbisher and repair-shop buy: the spread comes from grading working devices for resale, parting out cracked or locked units, and harvesting screens, batteries, and back glass for repair inventory. Per-pair economics support solid margins even when a portion lands in the parts bin. On intake, test each handset, verify IMEI status, check for activation lock, and sort into resale, repair, and parts tiers before pricing. Pickup is from the Jacksonville dock.', 210),
(null, 'authentic-jordan-sneakers-pallets', 'Premium Basketball Sneaker Pallet, 90 Pairs', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1300, 1300, 90, 14.44, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/authentic-jordan-sneakers-pallets-1.webp','/images/savemore/authentic-jordan-sneakers-pallets-2.webp','/images/savemore/authentic-jordan-sneakers-pallets-3.webp','/images/savemore/authentic-jordan-sneakers-pallets-4.webp','/images/savemore/authentic-jordan-sneakers-pallets-5.webp','/images/savemore/authentic-jordan-sneakers-pallets-6.webp','/images/savemore/authentic-jordan-sneakers-pallets-7.webp'], 'Ninety pairs of premium basketball sneakers come on an unmanifested customer-return pallet at $1,300, working out to roughly $14.44 per pair across retro and signature silhouettes in mixed sizes. The buyer here is an athletic-footwear reseller working booth tables, Saturday markets, sneaker consignment, and social channels where name-driven kicks move on visuals alone. At this per-pair cost, even a conservative average ticket clears strong margin once the lot is sorted by silhouette and condition. On intake, pair-match every box, check soles and uppers, separate retail-ready from clean-up, and grade by condition. Freight ships out of Jacksonville on standard pallet rates.', 211),
(null, 'home-depot-tool-pallets', 'Home Depot Tool Pallet, 40 to 45 Units', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1400, 1400, 43, 32.56, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/home-depot-tool-pallets-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested Home Depot customer-return pallet of roughly 43 mixed tools across cordless drills, drivers, saws, grinders, and hand tools from the major brands, priced at $1,400 or about $32.56 per unit. Tool resellers, hardware shops, and repair benches buy these to flip working units on Facebook Marketplace and OfferUp, list bare tools and chargers separately, and harvest batteries and accessories from non-working pieces. The per-unit cost leaves real room once a working drill or saw clears retail used pricing. On intake, bench-test every tool, sort by brand and platform, separate bare tools from kits, and price battery packs individually. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 212),
(null, 'woman-bags-purse-pallets', 'Women''s Handbags and Purses Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 900, 900, 1, 900, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/woman-bags-purse-pallets-1.webp'], 'A $900 unmanifested customer-return pallet of women''s handbags and purses spanning crossbody, shoulder, clutch, wristlet, backpack, and tote silhouettes in mixed colors and price tiers. This lot fits boutique resellers, market-table vendors, and online sellers running Poshmark, Mercari, and live-sale shows where bag turnover is steady and the category is season-proof, size-free, and forgiving on shipping. Inspected overstock and clean returns dominate, so the workflow is photo, list, and ship rather than heavy refurb. On intake, wipe down each bag, photograph hardware and lining, and tier inventory between boutique pricing and bin-store volume. Standard pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 213),
(null, 'wholesale-power-tools-pallets', 'Mixed-Brand Power Tools Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 750, 750, 1, 750, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/wholesale-power-tools-pallets-1.webp'], 'A $750 unmanifested customer-return pallet of mixed-brand power tools spanning corded and cordless drills, drivers, saws, and grinders from the major makers, plus bare tools, batteries, chargers, hand tools, and accessories. This is an entry-tier tool flipper buy: working units list to Facebook Marketplace and OfferUp, bare tools and batteries break out as their own SKUs, and non-working pieces feed a parts bin for chargers and accessory harvesting. Margins lean on disciplined testing and brand-platform sorting rather than volume. On intake, bench-test every unit, verify battery health, and tier between retail-ready, parts, and accessory pulls. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 214),
(null, 'buy-pallet-of-toilet-paper-1920-rolls-550', 'Toilet Paper Pallet, 1,920 Rolls', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 550, 550, 1, 550, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-pallet-of-toilet-paper-1920-rolls-550-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested overstock pallet of 1,920 rolls of bath tissue priced at $550, working out to roughly 29 cents per roll across standard and value brands in bulk and multipack retail formats. Bin stores, dollar shops, discount grocers, and route-based value resellers buy this category because it is sealed, has no expiry, never needs testing, and moves on price alone with repeat foot traffic. Per-roll economics leave a comfortable spread against any sub-dollar shelf price. On intake, verify pack integrity, sort by retail-ready multipacks versus loose stretch-wrapped product, and stage for shelf-ready presentation. Pickup is from the Jacksonville dock on standard pallet freight.', 215),
(null, 'buy-pallet-of-diapers-90-boxes', 'Baby Diapers Pallet, 90 Boxes', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 800, 800, 1, 800, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-pallet-of-diapers-90-boxes-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of 90 boxes of baby diapers priced at $800, spanning sizes from newborn through toddler across name brands and store-label product. Daycares, family-focused dollar stores, value resellers, and small neighborhood retailers buy this category because diaper demand is constant, price-insensitive, and recession-proof, and the lot ships sealed and shelf-ready with no testing required. The per-box cost of roughly $8.89 leaves consistent spread against typical retail multipack pricing. On intake, sort by size band, verify pack integrity, and group by brand so families can buy up a size or repeat-buy a brand. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 216),
(null, 'buy-wholesale-christmas-trees-50-trees-800', 'Artificial Christmas Trees Pallet, 50 Trees', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 800, 800, 1, 800, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-wholesale-christmas-trees-50-trees-800-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of 50 boxed artificial Christmas trees at $800, about $16 per tree, in a mix of sizes and styles with a likely blend of pre-lit and unlit units. Seasonal pop-up vendors, lot operators, holiday market sellers, and discount home retailers buy this category to load up ahead of November and clear through Christmas Eve on visual margin alone. Boxed product ships and stores flat, which keeps holding costs down for vendors timing a six-week window. On intake, verify branch integrity on a sample, plug-test any pre-lit units, and group by height tier for shelf presentation. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 217),
(null, 'buy-wholesale-victoria-secret-perfume-280-units', 'Victoria''s Secret Perfume Pallet, 280 Units', 'health-beauty', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1000, 1000, 280, 3.57, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-wholesale-victoria-secret-perfume-280-units-1.webp','/images/savemore/buy-wholesale-victoria-secret-perfume-280-units-2.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of 280 Victoria''s Secret body mists, fragrance sprays, eau de parfum, and rollerballs at $1,000, working out to about $3.57 per unit across an inspected mix that skews mostly sealed. Beauty resellers running live sales, TikTok Shop, Facebook live, weekend markets, and boutique shelves move this category fast on brand recognition alone, and the per-unit cost leaves wide spread against typical impulse-tier retail. The name carries the sale, so merchandising and lighting matter more than heavy listing copy. On intake, separate sealed from unsealed, group by scent family, and stage for camera-ready presentation. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 218),
(null, 'buy-wholesale-cat-food-by-the-pallet-45-bags-650', 'Wholesale Cat Food Pallet (45 Bags)', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 650, 650, 1, 650, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-wholesale-cat-food-by-the-pallet-45-bags-650-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of 45 bags of dry cat food priced at $650, spanning mixed brands and life-stage formulas across kitten, adult, and senior recipes. Discount pet shops, rescues, shelters, and value-focused neighborhood retailers buy this category because cat food is a recession-proof staple with repeat-purchase demand and price-insensitive buyers within each brand loyalty pocket. The defined 45-bag count makes margin math straightforward for resellers pricing against grocery shelves. On intake, verify bag integrity, check best-by dates, sort by life stage and brand, and pull any damaged bags for discounted clearance. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock on standard pallet freight.', 219),
(null, 'buy-wholesale-dog-food-by-the-pallet-40-bags-600', 'Wholesale Dog Food Pallet (40 Bags)', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 600, 600, 1, 600, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-wholesale-dog-food-by-the-pallet-40-bags-600-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of 40 bags of dry dog food at $600, spanning mixed brands and life-stage formulas covering puppy, adult, and senior recipes. Value resellers, small neighborhood pet retailers, rescues, and route-based vendors buy this category because dog food is a fast-moving, repeat-purchase staple where pricing against big-box and grocery shelves is the entire sale. The clean 40-bag count makes shelf math simple at $15 per bag landed. On intake, inspect every bag for tears, verify best-by dates, sort by brand and life stage, and pull any compromised bags for discounted clearance. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock on standard freight.', 220),
(null, 'buy-wholesale-dog-toys-by-the-pallet-500-units-550', 'Wholesale Dog Toys Pallet (500 Units)', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 750, 750, 500, 1.5, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-wholesale-dog-toys-by-the-pallet-500-units-550-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of 500 packaged dog toys at $750, working out to roughly $1.50 per unit across chew, rope, plush, squeaky, and fetch styles in mixed sizes. Pet boutiques, market-table vendors, dollar shops, and online sellers buy dog toys as a high-margin impulse category that keeps a storefront or live-sale show stocked with low-risk inventory. At a $1.50 per-unit cost, even sub-five-dollar retail pricing leaves room for steady spread. On intake, verify packaging integrity, separate by toy type and size, pull damaged blister packs for clearance, and bundle multi-pack offers for shelf or table presentation. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 221),
(null, 'wholesale-dog-food-pallets-for-sale-50-bags-cases-at-625', 'Wholesale Dog Food Pallet (50 Bags & Cases)', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 625, 625, 1, 625, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/wholesale-dog-food-pallets-for-sale-50-bags-cases-at-625-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of 50 bags and cases of dry dog food priced at $625, in a mix of brands and life-stage formulas covering puppy, adult, and senior recipes. Value resellers and small pet retailers serving routes, neighborhood storefronts, and shelter outlets buy this larger defined-count lot because dog food sells on price against grocery shelves and the repeat-purchase cycle keeps customers coming back. At $12.50 per unit landed, the math leaves real shelf spread. On intake, inspect every bag and case for damage, verify best-by dates, sort by brand and life stage, and pull any compromised pieces for clearance. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 222),
(null, 'buy-jordan-liquidation-pallets-50-pairs-at-650', 'Basketball Sneaker Liquidation Pallet (50 Pairs)', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 650.28, 650.28, 50, 13.01, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-jordan-liquidation-pallets-50-pairs-at-650-1.webp'], 'Fifty pairs of premium basketball sneakers arrive on an unmanifested customer-return pallet at $650.28, or about $13.01 per pair, in a uniform new-in-box presentation across retro and signature silhouettes. The buyer here is a first-time athletic-footwear reseller, weekend market vendor, or live-sale operator looking for an entry-tier sneaker lot where the consistent new-in-box condition removes most of the grading work. Per-pair economics leave a comfortable spread against the typical impulse retail price for branded kicks. On intake, pair-match every box, verify size labels against actual contents, sort by silhouette for camera-ready merchandising, and price by demand tier. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 223),
(null, 'buy-high-end-makeup-liquidation-pallets-200-premium-items-for-650', 'High-End Makeup Liquidation Pallet (200+ Items)', 'health-beauty', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 650.76, 650.76, 1, 650.76, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-high-end-makeup-liquidation-pallets-200-premium-items-for-650-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return pallet of more than 200 premium cosmetics priced at $650.76, covering prestige foundations, eye and lip product, palettes, and skincare from department-store and specialty beauty brands. Boutique beauty resellers, live-sale operators, and online sellers chasing prestige-tier spread buy this lot because the per-item cost lands near $3.25 and the resale ceiling sits well above what mass-market drugstore product can support. Brand recognition carries the listing, so photo quality and shade sorting drive turnover. On intake, separate sealed from unsealed, group by brand and product family, check for tester marks and seal integrity, and stage prestige product for camera-ready merchandising. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock.', 224),
(null, 'buy-zara-liquidation-pallets-500-pieces-for-1200', 'Zara Apparel Liquidation Pallet (500 Pieces)', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1200, 1200, 500, 2.4, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-zara-liquidation-pallets-500-pieces-for-1200-1.webp','/images/savemore/buy-zara-liquidation-pallets-500-pieces-for-1200-2.webp','/images/savemore/buy-zara-liquidation-pallets-500-pieces-for-1200-3.webp','/images/savemore/buy-zara-liquidation-pallets-500-pieces-for-1200-4.webp','/images/savemore/buy-zara-liquidation-pallets-500-pieces-for-1200-5.webp'], 'Five hundred pieces of customer-return Zara apparel across tops, dresses, knitwear, trousers, and outerwear in mixed men''s and women''s sizes, sold unmanifested as a single fashion lot. At $1,200 the pallet, cost lands at $2.40 a garment, which gives boutique resellers, IG live sellers, and weekend market vendors room to price trend-driven pieces aggressively and still hold healthy margin. Built-in name recognition shortens the sales pitch and helps clear knit and outerwear units faster than no-name fashion. On intake, sort by gender first, then by garment type and season, and pull damaged or heavily worn pieces straight into a B-grade bin before listing.', 225),
(null, 'buy-target-pallets-for-sale-1-pallet-550', 'Target Liquidation Pallet, Entry Tier', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 550.19, 550.19, 1, 550.19, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-target-pallets-for-sale-1-pallet-550-1.webp'], 'A single customer-return Target pallet of unmanifested general merchandise at $550.19, blending categories the chain actually ranges including home, kitchen, toys, beauty, apparel, and seasonal goods. This is the lowest-cost Target entry point in the catalog, built for first-time Target buyers, side-hustle resellers, and bin-store operators who want a controlled test before stepping up to multi-pallet loads. The cross-category mix also feeds flea-market tables and small storefronts that need variety more than depth. On intake, separate by department, pull anything sealed straight to fixed-price listings, and route opened or as-is items into a bin-store or live-sale pile.', 226),
(null, 'wholesale-makeup-products-pallet', 'Wholesale Makeup Products Pallet', 'health-beauty', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 500, 500, 1, 500, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/wholesale-makeup-products-pallet-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return cosmetics pallet at $500 covering complexion, eye, brow, lip, and cheek products plus brushes, sponges, and beauty tools sourced from US retail channels. The mix sits at a balanced mid-tier point with enough variety to stock a small beauty store, fill an IG live cart, or supply a flea-market beauty booth that needs constant rotation. Cross-sell is easy when you can pair a foundation with a setting tool or a lip with a liner from the same lot. On intake, separate sealed product from testers and opened items, check expiration codes, and discard anything past date before pricing.', 227),
(null, 'bedding-items-wholesale-pallet', 'Wholesale Bedding Pallet', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 400, 400, 1, 400, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/bedding-items-wholesale-pallet-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return home-textiles pallet at $400 covering sheet sets, comforters, quilts, duvet covers, blankets, and mattress protectors across sizes from twin through king. Bedding is an everyday essential with steady year-round demand from value resellers, discount home-goods stores, Airbnb hosts restocking units, and apartment-fillers shopping the weekend market. Larger sizes like queen and king typically clear at higher tickets than twin, so price by size class rather than a flat rate. On intake, inspect every item for stains, pet hair, and missing pillowcases, then wash and repackage anything return-worn before listing to lift perceived value.', 228),
(null, 'winter-jacket-wholesale-pallet', 'Wholesale Winter Jacket Pallet', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 800, 800, 1, 800, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/winter-jacket-wholesale-pallet-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return seasonal outerwear pallet at $800 of insulated and puffer jackets, parkas, coats, and shells spanning men''s, women''s, and kids'' sizes. Outerwear is the highest-ticket apparel category on the floor, with demand that spikes hard each fall and into winter, making this lot a strong play for resellers building cold-weather inventory ahead of the season. Boutique sellers, flea-market vendors, and Facebook Marketplace flippers can price individual coats well above generic apparel ticket levels. On intake, sort by size and gender first, check zippers, seams, and lining for damage, and stage heavier insulated pieces forward as temperatures drop.', 229),
(null, 'wholesale-pet-food-pallet', 'Wholesale Mixed Pet Food Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 500, 500, 1, 500, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/wholesale-pet-food-pallet-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return mixed pet food pallet at $500 covering dry dog and cat formulas across bag sizes plus treats and consumables that rotate in based on availability. One buy serves both major pet categories, which makes it a clean fit for general pet-focused value operations, neighborhood pet stores, and resellers running discount pet aisles at flea markets or bin stores. Pet owners shop on price and brand familiarity, so volume moves quickly when the price tag undercuts grocery and big-box. On intake, check every bag for date codes and seal integrity, separate dog from cat, and pull any swollen, leaking, or expired bags before listing.', 230),
(null, 'mixed-underwear-pallet', 'Mixed Underwear & Basics Pallet', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 500, 500, 1, 500, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/mixed-underwear-pallet-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return intimates pallet at $500 of new, packaged men''s and women''s underwear including briefs, boxers, bras, and bralettes across mixed sizes and styles. Because the units are sealed and unworn, this is a hygiene-appropriate everyday-essential buy that fits cleanly into value retailers, basics resellers, flea-market apparel tables, and bin-store rotations. Underwear sells on price point more than brand, so a low ticket and a clean display drive volume better than aggressive markup. On intake, separate men''s from women''s, then break down by size and style, and pull any opened, damaged, or torn packaging into a discount bin to keep the main inventory clean.', 231),
(null, 'buy-baby-diapers-wholesale-pallet-50-cases-at-500', 'Wholesale Baby Diapers Pallet (50 Cases)', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 500.42, 500.42, 1, 500.42, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-baby-diapers-wholesale-pallet-50-cases-at-500-1.webp'], 'Fifty cases of customer-return baby diapers at $500.42 covering mixed sizes from newborn through toddler across brand and store-label stock, sold unmanifested as a single sealed-goods lot. Diapers are a constant-demand baby essential that moves fast through value resellers, daycares, small neighborhood retailers, and parents shopping flea markets and Facebook Marketplace for a price break versus grocery aisles. Larger sizes typically turn faster because parents buy in bulk as kids grow. On intake, separate cases by size class, check every case for crushed corners and broken seals, and price by size tier rather than flat-rate to capture the premium on bigger packs.', 232),
(null, 'womens-underwear-pallet-500-pcs', 'Women''s Underwear Pallet (500 Pieces)', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 800, 800, 500, 1.6, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/womens-underwear-pallet-500-pcs-1.webp','/images/savemore/womens-underwear-pallet-500-pcs-2.webp'], 'Five hundred pieces of customer-return women''s intimates in new, packaged condition, covering briefs, panties, bras, bralettes, and lingerie across mixed sizes and styles, sold unmanifested as a single basics lot. At $800 the pallet, cost works out to roughly $1.60 a piece, which gives high-volume basics resellers, multi-pack flea-market vendors, and discount apparel storefronts room to price aggressively and still print solid margin. Sealed packaging keeps the lot hygiene-appropriate for retail display. On intake, sort by garment type first, then by size band, and pull any opened or damaged packaging into a separate discount bin to protect the main inventory presentation.', 233),
(null, 'wholesale-victorias-secret-underwear-pallet-1100-pieces', 'Victoria''s Secret Underwear Pallet (1,100 Pieces)', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1400, 1400, 1100, 1.27, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/wholesale-victorias-secret-underwear-pallet-1100-pieces-1.webp','/images/savemore/wholesale-victorias-secret-underwear-pallet-1100-pieces-2.webp','/images/savemore/wholesale-victorias-secret-underwear-pallet-1100-pieces-3.webp','/images/savemore/wholesale-victorias-secret-underwear-pallet-1100-pieces-4.webp'], 'Eleven hundred pieces of customer-return Victoria''s Secret and PINK intimates in new, packaged condition, covering panties, briefs, bras, bralettes, and loungewear across mixed sizes, sold unmanifested as one specialty-brand lot. At $1,400 the pallet, cost comes in under $1.30 a piece, and the brand name moves faster than generic intimates through IG live sellers, boutique apparel sellers, flea-market tables, and reseller booths that lean on recognized labels for impulse buys. Sealed packaging keeps every unit retail-presentable. On intake, sort by garment type and size, set bras and loungewear forward at higher price tiers, and route any opened or damaged packaging to a discount stack.', 234),
(null, 'stanley-tumblers-wholesale-pallets', 'Stanley Tumblers Wholesale Pallet', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 400, 400, 1, 400, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/stanley-tumblers-wholesale-pallets-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return drinkware pallet at $400 of Stanley insulated tumblers and travel mugs in assorted sizes, colors, and finishes, mixing overstock and shelf-pull condition. Drinkware tied to a hot brand turns fast on IG and TikTok live, Facebook Marketplace, and weekend market tables where buyers chase colors and limited finishes rather than shop on price alone. The lot suits resellers who already run live sales or have an audience watching for drops. On intake, group by size first then by color, pull any dented, scratched, or lid-damaged units into a B-grade bin, and stage the cleanest pieces forward for live-cart selection.', 235),
(null, 'wholesale-electronics-pallets', 'Wholesale Electronics Pallet', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 550, 550, 1, 550, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/wholesale-electronics-pallets-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return consumer-electronics pallet at $550 of audio, accessories, and small devices including headphones, earbuds, speakers, chargers, cables, power banks, and smart-home gadgets in mixed overstock, shelf-pull, and return condition. The value price point fits resellers comfortable with grading and testing, flea-market electronics tables, and eBay and Marketplace flippers who can price working sealed units above functional opened ones. Brand and category variety supports both bundle deals and individual listings. On intake, test every powered unit, separate sealed from opened, grade into working, cosmetic, and parts piles, and discard counterfeit-suspect items before listing.', 236),
(null, 'pallet-of-ipads', 'Apple iPad Pallet', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1400, 1400, 1, 1400, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/pallet-of-ipads-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return wholesale pallet at $1,400 of assorted Apple iPad models across recent generations, mixed storage sizes and finishes, sold as-is across working, cosmetic-flaw, and repair-candidate units. This is a refurbisher buy aimed at resellers with a test bench, a parts pipeline, and an eBay or Swappa channel where graded tablets command real ticket prices. Working units with clean screens print the margin, while screen-cracked or battery-tired bodies feed parts inventory or wholesale-to-repair-shop sales. On intake, verify Activation Lock status on every tablet first, then triage by working, repair, and parts before staging anything for listing.', 237),
(null, 'laptop-pallets-wholesale', 'Mixed-Brand Laptop Pallet', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1400, 1400, 1, 1400, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/laptop-pallets-wholesale-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return wholesale pallet at $1,400 of mixed-brand laptops spanning recent generations, with Windows machines plus Chromebook and Apple units in rotation, sold as-is across working, cosmetic-flaw, and repair-candidate grades. This is a refurbisher buy built for resellers with a test bench, a wipe-and-reload workflow, and a channel like eBay, Back Market, or local repair shops that pays a premium for graded units. Working machines drive margin, while broken-screen or no-boot units feed parts inventory or wholesale outs. On intake, boot and test every unit, wipe drives, check battery health, and triage into working, repair, and parts piles before listing.', 238),
(null, 'liquidation-cosmetics-pallets', 'Liquidation Cosmetics Pallet', 'health-beauty', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 550, 550, 1, 550, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/liquidation-cosmetics-pallets-1.webp'], 'An unmanifested customer-return beauty pallet at $550 of color cosmetics, skincare, haircare, tools, and bath items sourced from US retail channels, leaning toward sealed shelf-pull and overstock condition. The variety is broad enough to stock a beauty store, fill a flea-market booth, or feed an IG live cart where the host can rotate categories across sessions to keep the audience watching. Cross-selling skincare with color or haircare with tools lifts average ticket per buyer. On intake, separate sealed from opened, check expiration codes on every item, discard anything past date or tampered with, then group by category before pricing.', 239),
(null, 'authentic-nike-sneakers-pallet-125-pairs-bulk-nike-shoes', 'Athletic Sneaker Pallet (125 Pairs)', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1500, 1500, 130, 11.54, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/authentic-nike-sneakers-pallet-125-pairs-bulk-nike-shoes-1.webp','/images/savemore/authentic-nike-sneakers-pallet-125-pairs-bulk-nike-shoes-2.webp','/images/savemore/authentic-nike-sneakers-pallet-125-pairs-bulk-nike-shoes-3.webp'], 'This pallet lands 125 pairs of athletic sneakers in a mixed-grade, customer-return lot with no manifest, so styles, sizes, and conditions arrive as a working assortment rather than a curated run. At $1,500 the pallet, the math works out to roughly $11.54 per pair, leaving real margin for resellers who can sort and price quickly. Footwear at this cost point feeds bin stores, flea-market booths, swap-meet tables, and online sneaker sellers who lean on volume and broad-mix turnover. On intake, pair-match first, then triage by condition into A-grade ready-to-list, B-grade clean-and-sell, and parts. Local pickup at the Jacksonville dock is available.', 240),
(null, 'buy-ugg-shoes-pallet-150-pairs', 'Sheepskin Boot & Slipper Pallet (150 Pairs)', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1400, 1400, 150, 9.33, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-ugg-shoes-pallet-150-pairs-1.webp','/images/savemore/buy-ugg-shoes-pallet-150-pairs-2.webp','/images/savemore/buy-ugg-shoes-pallet-150-pairs-3.webp'], '150 pairs of sheepskin boots, slippers, and casual footwear arrive on this customer-return pallet, spanning men''s, women''s, and kids'' sizes in unmanifested form. At $1,400 the lot, the per-pair cost lands near $9.33, which gives resellers room to absorb the inevitable singles and grade-B pairs while still pricing competitively. Sheepskin styling pulls well at swap meets, consignment shops, seasonal pop-ups, and online resale, especially heading into colder months when slippers and tall boots move fast. On intake, match pairs first, brush and air out the sheepskin, then split into retail-ready, clean-and-sell, and parts. Dock pickup is available in Jacksonville.', 241),
(null, 'buy-microwave-pallets', 'Countertop Microwave Pallet', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1400, 1400, 1, 1400, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-microwave-pallets-1.webp'], 'This pallet carries an assortment of countertop microwave ovens across sizes, wattages, and brands in customer-return and overstock condition, sold unmanifested as a single pallet buy at $1,400. Microwaves remain a steady appliance category for local Facebook Marketplace flips, OfferUp listings, dollar-store style discount shops, and apartment-turnover landlords restocking units between tenants. The mix usually yields working sets, cosmetic-only blems, and a handful of repair candidates. On intake, power-test each unit on a dedicated outlet, run a thirty-second water-cup heat check, then inspect turntable, door latch, and keypad. Sort into A, B, and parts. Local pickup is available at the Jacksonville dock.', 242),
(null, 'wholesale-tv-pallets-10-mixed-tvs-32-to-85-inches-900', 'Mixed TV Pallet (10 TVs, 32 to 85 Inches)', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 900, 900, 1, 900, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/wholesale-tv-pallets-10-mixed-tvs-32-to-85-inches-900-1.webp'], 'Ten mixed televisions ride this pallet, ranging from 32-inch sets up to 85-inch panels across various brands, panel types, and smart platforms in customer-return condition. At $900 the pallet, the effective cost is roughly $90 per set, which leaves working units profitable even after refurb time and the inevitable cracked panel pulled for parts. High-ticket TVs sell strong on local Facebook Marketplace, OfferUp, and in-person at Jacksonville-area pop-ups where buyers can preview the picture before paying. On intake, power-test each set, check ports and remotes, then sort into working, cosmetic-blem, and parts-only. Local dock pickup is available.', 243),
(null, 'buy-macbook-pallet-10-to-20-units-from-1900', 'Apple MacBook Pallet (10 to 20 Units)', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 1900, 1900, 20, 95, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/buy-macbook-pallet-10-to-20-units-from-1900-1.webp'], 'Between 10 and 20 Apple MacBook Air and Pro laptops fill this pallet, spanning Intel and Apple-silicon generations in mixed customer-return condition with no manifest. At $1,900 starting, the per-unit cost lands near $95, which gives refurbishers room to invest in batteries, displays, and keyboards while still hitting healthy resale margins on eBay, Swappa, and Back Market. The buyer profile here is a working refurbisher, not a general bin-store operator. On intake, check Activation Lock status immediately, log serials, run diagnostics, and split into resale-ready, refurb-needed, and parts. Local Jacksonville pickup is available, or freight can be quoted to your shop.', 244),
