(null, 'e-scooters', 'Assorted Electric Scooters Pallet', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 2072, 2072, 1, 2072, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/e-scooters-1.webp'], 'This pallet brings an assortment of electric scooters across a mix of brands and models in customer-return condition, sold as-is and unmanifested. Expect working units, cosmetic-only blems, and repair candidates in the mix at $2,072 the pallet. The buyer here is a refurbisher or local marketplace flipper, since charged-and-tested units sell strong on Facebook Marketplace, OfferUp, and Craigslist where buyers want to test-ride before purchase, and even non-working scooters carry real parts value in batteries, controllers, and decks. On intake, charge each unit overnight, test throttle and brakes, then triage into ready-to-sell, refurb, and parts. Local Jacksonville pickup is available.', 254),
(null, 'target-tg19', 'Target TG19 Unmanifested Single Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 554, 554, 1, 554, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/target-tg19-1.webp'], 'Target TG19 ships as a single unmanifested customer-return pallet of general merchandise, contents unknown until the wrap comes off. Expect a cross-category mix typical of Target single-pallet inventory: housewares, seasonal, smalls, and soft goods, with Sterilite plastic storage totes a common addition to these loads. The format suits bin-store operators, flea-market sellers, and online resellers who price by the piece and recover value across many small tickets rather than a few big ones. Plan a same-day intake to grade returns, group sellable items by category, and pull damages so the floor or listings stay clean. Available for dock pickup in Jacksonville or freight out.', 255),
