(null, 'target-tg20', 'Target TG20 Unmanifested Single Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 662, 662, 1, 662, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/target-tg20-1.webp'], 'Target TG20 arrives as one unmanifested customer-return pallet of cross-category general merchandise, contents unknown until the load is broken down. Expect the standard Target single-pallet pattern of housewares, seasonal, smalls, and soft goods, with Sterilite plastic storage totes a frequent inclusion. The mix works for bin stores, flea-market booths, and online resellers who price across many small tickets rather than chasing single hero items. Run a same-day intake to grade returns into sellable, repackage, and damage tiers, then list higher-ticket pieces individually while bin-pricing the rest. Dock pickup in Jacksonville or freight booked out to your location.', 257),
