(null, 'tires-10-total', 'Mixed Tires Lot (10 Total)', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 420, 420, 1, 420, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/tires-10-total-1.webp'], 'This lot is ten assorted tires across mixed sizes and brands, in new, takeoff, and used condition, sold unmanifested as a single pallet of general merchandise. The format fits local tire shops, independent installers, and Marketplace resellers who match pairs or sets to walk-in customers and price by tread depth rather than retail. Demand stays steady year-round in any market with daily drivers. Inspect tread depth, sidewall condition, and DOT date codes on intake, then sort by size and grade so pairs and matched sets are easy to pull. Pickup from the Jacksonville dock or freight quoted to your address.', 261),
