(null, 'bj-s-seasonal-christmas-easter', 'BJ''s Christmas & Easter Seasonal Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 440, 440, 1, 440, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/bj-s-seasonal-christmas-easter-1.webp'], 'This BJ''s Wholesale Club pallet bundles dual-holiday seasonal merchandise: Christmas decor and gifts on one side, Easter and spring goods plus party items on the other, all unmanifested customer-return and overstock. Condition will vary by box, with some shelf-pull and some opened-return mixed in. It works for seasonal pop-ups, holiday markets, and Marketplace sellers who can hold inventory between windows and time the listings, giving one buy two distinct demand cycles to sell into. At $440 for the pallet, the play is patience: list Christmas in October-November and Easter in February-March. On intake, split immediately into two labeled holiday totes and shelf separately so the off-season stock stays clean. Dock pickup available.', 275),
(null, 'double-stacked-random', 'Double-Stacked Mixed Merchandise Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 270, 270, 1, 270, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/double-stacked-random-1.webp'], 'This is roughly two pallets of mixed general merchandise stacked into one load, covering home, kitchen, accessories, toys, seasonal, and small electronics in customer-return and overstock condition. Manifest is not provided, so plan on a working sort across the full double-stack. The buyer profile is bin-store operators, flea-market vendors, and high-volume Marketplace flippers who want maximum piece count and category variety at a single cost-of-goods entry. At $270 for the doubled load, the per-pallet basis is low enough to leave room for shrink and unsellables. On intake, break the stack down by category into labeled totes before grading anything, so the second pallet does not bury the first. Forklift dock pickup.', 276),
(null, 'craft-sewing', 'Craft & Sewing Supplies Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 270, 270, 1, 270, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/craft-sewing-1.webp'], 'This focused customer-return and overstock pallet is built around craft and sewing inventory: thread, needles, bobbins, trims, fabric cuts, yarn, and assorted maker tools, sold unmanifested as a category lot. Condition is mixed return and shelf-pull, so expect some opened packages alongside sealed stock. The natural buyers are quilters, sewists, homeschool families, and craft-fair vendors reached through Etsy supply listings, Facebook craft groups, and weekend market booths where category-clustered booths outperform random mixes. At $270 for the pallet, the math works if the load is broken into kits or grab-bags rather than sold piece by piece. On intake, sort by craft type, then assemble themed $10-$15 bundles. Standard dock pickup.', 277),
(null, 'temu-pallet', 'Temu Overstock & Returns Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 810, 810, 1, 810, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/temu-pallet-1.webp'], 'This is a high-piece-count pallet of unmanifested customer-return and overstock merchandise in the Temu-style category mix: small gadgets, electronic accessories, home and kitchen items, costume jewelry, hand tools, and novelty goods. Item count is high and average retail per piece is low, so condition triage matters more than individual grading. The buyer profile is bin-store operators and dollar-tier flea-market sellers who turn dense piece counts into ticket volume at $1-$5 price points. At $810 for the pallet, the recovery model depends on bin throughput rather than hero finds. On intake, sort by category into bin-ready totes and pull anything battery-powered for a quick function test. Forklift dock pickup available.', 278),
(null, 'mail-stacked-pallet', 'Stacked Undelivered Mail Parcel Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 800, 800, 1, 800, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/mail-stacked-pallet-1.webp'], 'This stacked pallet is built from undelivered and returned mail parcels, each box a separate original order still in shipping packaging, with a cross-category mix of electronics, home, beauty, toys, and accessories. Manifest is not provided and contents are unknown until unboxing, which is the entire point of the format. The natural channel is unboxing-driven resale: Whatnot live mystery-box shows, TikTok Live reveals, and eBay surprise lots where the discovery moment drives bids. At $800 for the stacked load, the recovery depends on staging the unboxing for camera rather than ripping boxes in the back room. On intake, count parcels, pull anything obviously damaged for separate handling, and queue the rest for live segments. Forklift dock pickup.', 279),
(null, 'bj-s-wholesale-soft-goods', 'BJ''s Soft Goods Pallet', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 220, 220, 1, 220, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/bj-s-wholesale-soft-goods-1.webp'], 'This BJ''s Wholesale Club pallet is a soft-goods load of textiles, apparel, and home linens including clothing, bedding, towels, and fabric items, much of it in club-format multipacks. It is unmanifested customer-return and overstock, so condition runs from sealed multipacks to opened returns that need a wash before listing. The buyer profile is broad: apparel resellers, Marketplace household sellers, and flea-market vendors who like easy-handling, lightweight inventory that ships cheap and does not break. At $220 for the pallet, the cost basis leaves room to bundle slower pieces with stronger ones. On intake, separate sealed multipacks from opened returns and shelf them apart so the new-in-package stock is not picked over. Dock pickup available.', 280),
(null, 'plastic-fuel-tanks', 'Plastic Fuel Tanks Wholesale Lot', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 310, 310, 1, 310, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/plastic-fuel-tanks-1.webp'], 'This parts-driven lot consists of replacement plastic fuel tanks in mixed sizes and fitments covering automotive, marine, powersports, and small-equipment applications, sold unmanifested as customer-return and overstock stock. Condition is mostly shelf-pull and inspected return, so the value is in matching part numbers to vehicle and engine fitments rather than cosmetic resale. The natural buyer is a parts reseller, marine and powersports shop, or eBay Motors specialist who can decode model fit and list against active demand searches. At $310 for the lot, the recovery depends on identifying the higher-fitment tanks first. On intake, photograph any part-number labels or molded markings, log fitment to a spreadsheet, then shelf by application. Dock pickup.', 281),
(null, 'bj-s-clothing-christmas', 'BJ''s Christmas Apparel Pallet', 'apparel', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 728, 728, 1, 728, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/bj-s-clothing-christmas-1.webp'], 'This BJ''s Wholesale Club pallet is a larger seasonal apparel buy focused on Christmas-themed clothing: festive sweaters, holiday pajamas, family matching sets, and themed pieces across men''s, women''s, and kids. It is unmanifested customer-return and overstock, so expect a mix of sealed multipacks and opened returns needing a quick steam or wash. The buyer profile is seasonal pop-up operators, holiday-market vendors, and Whatnot apparel sellers who run live shows through November and into mid-December where festive pieces move on impulse. At $728 for the pallet, the window is short, so list early and price for sell-through. On intake, sort by size and family-set groupings, then photograph the strongest pieces for a launch drop. Dock pickup.', 282),
(null, 'dragons-3d-printed', 'Articulated 3D Printed Dragons Lot', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 445, 445, 1, 445, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/dragons-3d-printed-1.webp'], 'This novelty lot contains articulated, flexible 3D printed dragons in mixed colors and sizes, sold as a customer-return and overstock-style load with no manifest. The pieces are lightweight resin or filament prints, so check joints for snapped links and pull any with broken articulation for repair or scrap. The buyer profile is live sellers and gift-shop resellers reached through TikTok Shop, Whatnot, Mercari, and weekend market booths where fidget toys photograph well in short-form video and clear at $8-$20 impulse price points. At $445 for the lot, the math works on volume sell-through during a content push. On intake, grade by color and size, photograph a hero piece per color for the listing thumbnail. Dock pickup.', 283),
(null, 'hair-tools-pallet', 'Hair Tools Pallet', 'health-beauty', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 270, 270, 1, 270, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/hair-tools-pallet-1.webp'], 'This focused beauty pallet is built around powered styling tools: blow dryers, flat irons, curling wands, clippers, trimmers, and assorted accessories across mixed brands, sold unmanifested as a customer-return, shelf-pull, and overstock load. Condition varies, so plan to plug-test every powered unit before listing and route non-working pieces to parts or scrap. The natural buyer is a beauty-supply reseller, barber-shop operator, or eBay and Marketplace seller who can verify function and list with a working-condition note. At $270 for the pallet, the recovery hinges on test yield rather than top-line retail. On intake, set up a test station with a surge strip, sort working units from non-working immediately, and photograph the clean ones individually. Dock pickup.', 284),
(null, 'kitchen-sink-pallet-11-units-total', 'Kitchen Sink Pallet (11 Units)', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 380, 380, 11, 34.55, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/kitchen-sink-pallet-11-units-total-1.webp'], 'Eleven kitchen sinks bundled into a single home-improvement lot, customer-return and unmanifested, with an assortment of single-bowl, double-bowl, drop-in, and undermount styles across stainless, composite, and other materials. At $380 for the pallet, that''s roughly $34.55 per fixture, a workable number for remodelers, handyman crews, plumbers, and small contractors who can move individual sinks through Facebook Marketplace, OfferUp, or a builder''s supply yard. The fixed unit count makes pricing simple by piece. On intake, uncrate each sink, check basin and faucet-hole condition, and stage by size and mount type so contractors can shop the pallet quickly at pickup.', 285),
(null, 'christmas-tree-pallet-small-white-trees', 'Small White Christmas Trees Pallet', 'houseware', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 300, 300, 1, 300, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/christmas-tree-pallet-small-white-trees-1.webp'], 'A seasonal customer-return pallet of small white artificial Christmas trees in assorted compact and tabletop sizes, boxed and packed for display. Contents are unmanifested, so expect a mix of styles suited to apartments, dorm rooms, office desks, retail counters, and accent corners rather than full-room centerpieces. At $300 for the pallet, the play is to stock ahead of the holiday window and move units through pop-up booths, flea markets, holiday craft shows, eBay, or Facebook Marketplace where seasonal decor turns fast. On intake, open boxes, fluff a sample tree per style to confirm condition, then store flat and dry until the Q4 selling season opens.', 286),
(null, 'hardware-pallet-hundreds-of-items', 'Hardware Pallet, Hundreds of Items', 'general-merchandise', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 270, 270, 1, 270, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/hardware-pallet-hundreds-of-items-1.webp'], 'A high-count hardware lot of hundreds of small home-improvement pieces packed into one pallet: fasteners, fittings, brackets, hinges, fixtures, hand tools, and assorted accessories. Customer-return and unmanifested condition, with much of the stock appearing new or shelf-pull and easy to price by the piece, the bin, or the pound. At $270 for the pallet, the resale angle is flea markets, swap meets, hardware flippers, eBay lot sellers, and small contractors who buy odd-lot fasteners by weight. On intake, dump and sort into bins by category, scrap anything rusted or incomplete, then bag mixed lots for table sales at the next weekend market.', 287),
(null, 'mixed-electronics-pallet', 'Mixed Consumer Electronics Pallet', 'electronics', 'unmanifested', 'customer-return', 520, 520, 1, 520, 'in-stock', array['/images/savemore/mixed-electronics-pallet-1.webp'], 'A mixed consumer electronics pallet with assorted gadgets, accessories, and small devices, likely spanning audio, smart-home, lighting, charging, and similar categories. Condition is customer return and the load is unmanifested, so plan on a working, partial, and scrap split that only reveals itself at the table. At $520 for the pallet, the angle is testing aggressively on intake: a handful of working higher-ticket items can carry the lot through eBay, Mercari, or a local electronics resale shop, while broken pieces feed parts buyers and scrap recyclers. Set up a test bench with cables and chargers before unloading, and grade each unit by working, fixable, or parts.', 288)
